title: PostgreSQL: Instances
agents: linux
catalog: app/postgresql
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the instances of a PostgreSQL database as well as their PostgreSQL versions.

 If instance is running, service status is OK, otherwise CRIT.

 This check needs the Checkmk mk_postgres plug-in installed in the agent.

item:
 Name of the database in upper case letters

discovery:
 One service is created for each instance.
